Package: modeltuner
Title: A toolkit for model evaluation, model comparison and hyperparameter tuning based on cross-validation
Version: 0.0.10
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: stats, MetricsWeighted, glmnet, xgboost (>= 1.5), ggplot2, matrixStats, RANN, progress
Suggests: lme4, robustbase, mgcv, rpart, quantreg, ranger, magrittr, tibble, knitr, rmarkdown, MASS, gridExtra
Authors@R: person("Mathias", "Ambuehl", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), email = "mathias.ambuehl@consultag.ch")
Maintainer: Mathias Ambuehl <mathias.ambuehl@consultag.ch>
Description: A toolkit for easy model evaluation, model comparison and hyperparameter tuning based on cross-validation is provided. It applies to models for a continuous or binary response that are generated with the formula interface. In addition, it includes functionalities for conveniently fitting and tuning glmnet and xgboost models.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://mathiasambuehl.github.io/modeltuner/
